TestNumbers = input()
counter = 1
while counter <= int(TestNumbers):
    (S, SG, FG, D, T) = map(int, input().split())
    OCS = S + D * 180 / T
    SGR = abs(SG - OCS)
    FGR = abs(FG - OCS)
    if SGR < FGR:
        print('SEBI')
    elif FGR < SGR:
        print('FATHER')
    else:
        print('DRAW')
    counter += 1

t = int(input())
for i in range(t):
    (s, sg, fg, d, t) = map(int, input().split())
    dis = d * 50
    speed = dis * 3.6 / t
    actualspeed = s + speed
    a = abs(actualspeed - sg)
    b = abs(actualspeed - fg)
    if a < b:
        print('SEBI')
    elif b < a:
        print('FATHER')
    elif a == b:
        print('DRAW')

for i in range(int(input())):
    (s, sg, fg, d, t) = [int(i) for i in input().split()]
    dis = d * 50
    speed = dis / t
    exs = speed * 18 / 5
    ts = s + exs
    ss = abs(sg - ts)
    sf = abs(fg - ts)
    if ss > sf:
        print('FATHER')
    elif ss < sf:
        print('SEBI')
    elif ss == sf:
        print('DRAW')
